: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Once turned on, descriptive audio will stay on until its turned off</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Most movies and TV shows don’t have descriptive audio, in those cases the movie will play normally.</span></p></li></ul><br><br><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">You can check to see what movies and shows on netflix have descriptive audio here: <a href="da-platform.php"><u>http://go-from-here.com/da-platform.php</u></a></span></span><div><br><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-7df5891e-7fff-229c-a5fc-a6083982975f"><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Every profile has different settings and changing one profiles settings will not change the other profile settings. </span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">When you change profile settings on one platform (web browser, playstation, smart TV, {hopefully Xbox I don’t have one so I can't test this} etc.) The settings will be the same if you switch to a different platform.</span></p></li></ul><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><b>Making the change on your computer's web browser</b></span></p><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Select a movie with descriptive audio</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2b4db036-7fff-9f8f-cde3-3c387e2d17cc"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">While the video is playing select the subtitles menu </span></span><br></span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-724310a8-7fff-e59e-f13f-c6c403549c2b"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">In the subtitle menu click “English- Audio Description</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">Resume play</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">You will now have descriptive audio on all netflix programs that have Descriptive Audio until you choose to turn it off by selecting "english" in your subtitles menu </span><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></span><span style="background-color: inherit; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><br><br></span></p></li></ul><div><br></div></span></div></div></div><div id="i4"><div id="i5"><figure id="ozplayer-1-container" class="ozplayer-container"><div data-responsive="ozplayer-1-container" data-controls="stack" class="ozplayer" id="ozplayer-1"><video controls="controls" preload="none"><source src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BIwfQUqOSbY" type="video/x-youtube"><div class="ozplayer-fallback"><ul><li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BIwfQUqOSbY">Video for playback</a></li></ul></div></video></div></figure><script type="text/javascript" src="https://ozplayer.global.ssl.fastly.net/3.5/ozplayer-core/ozplayer.free.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="https://ozplayer.global.ssl.fastly.net/3.5/ozplayer-lang/en.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="https://ozplayer.global.ssl.fastly.net/3.5/config.js"></script></div></div></div><div id="i6"><div id="i7"><ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin-left: 36pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">Watch me turn AD on here: </span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://youtu.be/BIwfQUqOSbY">https://youtu.be/BIwfQUqOSbY</a></span></p></li></ul><div style=""><br></div><div style="">Trouble shooting</div><ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">If descriptive audio it is possible the movie or show you are watching doesn’t have descriptive audio. Check the Descriptive Audio Netflix link to make sure the movie you want to watch has descriptive audio.</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;">If you have turned on descriptive audio and you are sure the movie you have chosen has descriptive audio but descriptive audio isn’t working. Check your profile, it is possible that the profile you are in the wrong profile.</span></p></li></ul></div></div><div id="footer"><div 